des:
AiHub Smart products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your AiHub smart plugs.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your smart plugs - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your AiHub Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "AiHub Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "AiHub Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some AiHub Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "AiHub Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "AiHub Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "AiHub Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "AiHub Smart", and you'll be navigated to "AiHub Smart" login page;
(9). Input your Replace your App name account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
“Alexa,turn on the plug.”
“Alexa,turn off the plug.”
